POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (06): GLOBAL ACUTE FLACCID PARALYSIS, WPV1 (MALAWI ex PAKISTAN), CVDPV1 (MADAGASCAR), CVDV2 (DEMOCRATIC REPUBLIC OF CONGO, NIGERIA, YEMEN), REQUEST FOR INFORMATION
